Package projects.spatial.trees

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    SpatialDictionary
    SpatialDictionary is an abstraction over any data structure that could be used to allow efficient insertion, deletion and search of KDPoints.
    SpatialQuerySolver
    SpatialQuerySolver is an interface that declares methods for range and k-NN queries over KDPoints.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    KDTree
    KDTree implements K-D Trees, where K is a positive integer that defines the dimensionality of the space.
    PRQuadTree
    PRQuadTree implements Point-Region (P-R) QuadTrees.
